---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Research
permalink: /research/
---

<h1>Research</h1>
<p class="lede narrow">My work sits between analysis, computation, geometry, and mathematical physics. The themes below are intentionally concise; they are meant to orient readers rather than replace papers or notes.</p>

<div class="stack">
  {% for area in research %}
    <section class="rule-section">
      <h2>{{ area.title }}</h2>
      <p>{{ area.summary }}</p>
      <p class="meta">{{ area.status }}. {{ area.keywords | join(", ") }}.</p>
    </section>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<section class="rule-section">
  <h2>Talks</h2>
  <p>Selected talks and seminars from the research archive.</p>
  <ol class="pub-list compact-list">
    {% for talk in talks %}
      <li>
        <strong>{{ talk.title }}</strong>
        <span>{% if talk.year %}{{ talk.year }}. {% endif %}{{ talk.description }}</span>
        {% if talk.links and talk.links.length %}
          <span class="links">
            {% for link in talk.links %}
              <a href="{{ link.url }}">{{ link.label }}</a>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </span>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>
